Enjoy gallon door storage, Humidity Controlled Crisper Drawers for fruits and vegetables and a Deli Drawer for deli meats and cheeses. Pure Source 3 filtration gives you great-tasting, clean water and ice. Smudge-Proof Stainless Steel offers a protective coating that inhibits fingerprints and smudges. Plus Corner-to-corner LED lighting throughout the refrigerator for better visibility.

309424632.Title: Cafe 25.2 cu. ft. Smart Built-In Side by Side Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Silver
309424632.Description: One look at the Cafe kitchen and youll feel as if youve been transported behind the scenes of your favorite casual dining experience. Each appliance has been meticulously designed to create an atmosphere where people like to gather and love to cook. Tough stainless steel and powerful elements complement their robust appearance.

316293601.Title: Frigidaire 33 in. 22.3 cu. ft. Standard Depth Side by Side Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Silver
316293601.Description: This Frigidaire 33" Side-by-side refrigerator offers our EvenTemp™ Cooling System which reacts quickly to temperature fluctuations and constantly circulates cold air throughout the fresh food and freezer compartments, ensuring a consistent cool from top to bottom. Color: Stainless Steel.

311349682.Title: KitchenAid 19.8 cu. ft. Side by Side Refrigerator in Black Stainless Steel with Print Shield, Counter Depth, Black Stainless with PrintShield Finish
311349682.Description: This 19.9 cu. ft. side-by-side refrigerator features the Preserva Food Care System. Its 2 independent cooling systems help keep food fresh while the FreshFlow Air Filter minimizes odors, and the Produce Preserver delays over-ripening. The counter-depth design gives the high-end look of built-in refrigerators and the PrintShield Finish resists fingerprints and smudges on the stainless exterior. Color: Black Stainless with PrintShield Finish.

316039934.Title: FRIGIDAIRE GALLERY 22.3 cu. ft. 36 in. Counter Depth Side by Side Refrigerator in Smudge-Proof Black Stainless Steel, Silver
316039934.Description: This Frigidaire Gallery 36" Counter-Depth Side-by-side refrigerator offers our advanced CrispSeal® Plus Crisper. This crisper keeps produce fresh with a seal that blocks out dry air, plus an added filter reduces the gas that causes produce to ripen faster. It also features our EvenTemp™ Cooling System which keeps your food fresh by reacting quickly to temperature fluctuations and constantly circulates cold air throughout the fresh food and freezer compartments, ensuring a consistent cool from top to bottom. Color: Stainless Steel.

300503858.Title: 23.2 cu. ft. Side-By-Side Refrigerator in Bisque, ENERGY STAR
300503858.Description: GE appliances provide up-to-date technology and exceptional quality to simplify the way you live. With a timeless appearance, this family of appliances is ideal for your family. And, coming from one of the most trusted names in America, you know that this entire selection of appliances is as advanced as it is practical. Color: Bisque.

301991272.Title: Whirlpool 28 cu. ft. Side by Side Refrigerator in Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel
301991272.Description: Store more of your family's favorites with purposeful storage spaces. This extra-large refrigerator features IN-DOOR-ICE storage to give you an extra full shelf in the freezer. Get convenient access to filtered water with the exterior ice and water dispenser with EVERYDROP filtration. Plus, our side-by-side refrigerator's ACCU-CHILL temperature management system keeps family favorites in their ideal environment with quick cooling. Color: Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel.

311564186.Title: KitchenAid 36 in. W 24.8 cu. ft. Side by Side Refrigerator with Exterior Ice and Water in PrintShield Stainless Steel, Stainless Steel with PrintShield Finish
311564186.Description: This 24.8 cu. ft. side-by-side refrigerator features the Preserva Food Care System. Its two independent cooling systems help keep food fresh while the FreshFlow Air Filter minimizes odors, and the Produce Preserver delays over-ripening. PrintShield Finish on the stainless steel exterior resists fingerprints and smudges for easy cleaning. Color: Stainless Steel with PrintShield Finish.
